marshal_operator_envelope_supplement_json(...) emits the same fields except
dispatch_state, because prepare/rollout already expose dispatch_state directly.

prepare operator packet:
  tool = hero.marshal.prepare
  schema_version = kikijyeba.marshal.prepare.v2.5b
  next_safe_actions = [step.next_action]
